    <h2>Overview</h2>
    <p>This website respects your privacy and collects only limited, anonymous usage statistics to understand how the site is used and to improve its content and performance.</p>
 
    <h2>Analytics</h2>
    <p>This website uses Umami Analytics to collect anonymous usage data.</p>
    <p>The information collected may include:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Pages visited</li>
      <li>Referring websites</li>
      <li>Browser type and version</li>
      <li>Operating system</li>
      <li>Device type</li>
      <li>Country or general geographic region</li>
      <li>Date and time of visits</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Umami does not use cookies and does not collect personally identifiable information such as your name, email address, or full IP address.</p>
    <p>The analytics data is used solely to understand website traffic and improve the website.</p>
 
    <h2>Cookies</h2>
    <p>This website does not use cookies for analytics or tracking purposes.</p>
 
    <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p>This website may load assets or content from third-party services, such as fonts, CDNs, or embedded media. These services may receive technical information such as your IP address as part of delivering content.</p>
    <p>Please refer to the privacy policies of those providers for more information.</p>
 
    <h2>Your Rights</h2>
    <p>Depending on your location, you may have rights regarding your personal data under applicable privacy laws, including the right to request information about any personal data processed about you.</p>
    <p>If you have any questions about this privacy policy, you may contact:</p>
    <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:contact@hmistudios.com">contact@hmistudios.com</a></p>
 
